1317
01:28:41.500 --> 01:28:43.291
"The needs of the many…"

1318
01:28:43.833 --> 01:28:46.125
[solemn music playing]

1319
01:28:51.875 --> 01:28:54.041
"…outweigh the needs of the few."

1320
01:28:55.041 --> 01:28:56.500
[breathes shakily]

1321
01:28:57.625 --> 01:28:59.250
[sighs softly]

1322
01:29:00.375 --> 01:29:02.333
Please. Siggy. tell our little miracle

1323
01:29:02.416 --> 01:29:03.291
that papa was...

