01:29:03.375 --> 01:29:04.458
[Sigrid gasps]

1325
01:29:15.041 --> 01:29:16.708
That Papa…

1326
01:29:17.791 --> 01:29:19.541
[grunting]

1327
01:29:32.416 --> 01:29:34.250
That Papa was…

1328
01:29:37.291 --> 01:29:39.291
[epic orchestral music playing]

1329
01:29:46.416 --> 01:29:47.833
[music fades]

1330
01:29:47.916 --> 01:29:49.250
…Superman.

1331
01:29:50.166 --> 01:29:52.166
[heartbeat thumping]

1332
01:29:58.791 --> 01:30:00.791
