1373
01:33:39.541 --> 01:33:40.541
[thumping]

1374
01:33:42.500 --> 01:33:43.791
And a hope

1375
01:33:44.500 --> 01:33:46.500
to find one's way back.

1376
01:33:47.916 --> 01:33:52.083
Back to a place where one can feel free.

1377
01:33:52.166 --> 01:33:54.000
[bellowing]

1378
01:33:56.375 --> 01:33:59.333
A place to call…

1379
01:34:01.208 --> 01:34:02.416
Home.

1380
01:34:02.500 --> 01:34:04.500
[uplifting music rises]

1381
01:34:16.125 --> 01:34:18.291
