1390
01:35:01.250 --> 01:35:02.333
but. uh…

1391
01:35:03.583 --> 01:35:06.666
Just… give it some time.

1392
01:35:07.583 --> 01:35:08.458
Mm.

1393
01:35:08.541 --> 01:35:09.708
[dark music playing]

1394
